---
// Hub for hero direction samples (static HTML lives in public/samples/)
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BaxterLabs — Hero samples</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;1,9..40,400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: #0c0c0e;
        color: #e8e6e3;
        min-height: 100vh;
        line-height: 1.6;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }

      .wrap {
        max-width: 52rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      }

      .label {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #8a8782;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .intro {
        color: #a8a5a0;
        font-size: 1rem;
        max-width: 36rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      a.card {
        display: block;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
        background: #141416;
        border: 1px solid #252528;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      }

      a.card:hover {
        border-color: #3a3a3f;
        background: #18181b;
      }

      a.card h2 {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      }

      a.card p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #8a8782;
      }

      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #c9a227;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .tag.b {
        color: #e07a5f;
      }

      .tag.c {
        color: #a8a5a0;
      }

      .tag.d {
        color: #6bc97a;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #6b6966;
        margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
      }

      .note {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #252528;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #6b6966;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="label">Session 1 — pick a direction</p>
      <h1>Hero visual samples</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Compare combinations below (hero v2), then original A/B/C. Same copy on all. Resize for mobile.
      </p>

      <p class="section-title">C refinements — typography direction</p>
      <p class="intro" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: -0.5rem;">
        You picked Sample C. Three refinements — live homepage uses <strong>C-proof</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-c-pure.html">
          <span class="tag c">C-pure</span>
          <h2>Typography-first</h2>
          <p>Mesh · big type · white CTA · no diagram · Instrument Sans · most editorial</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-c-warm.html">
          <span class="tag b">C-warm</span>
          <h2>Typography + coral</h2>
          <p>Line stagger · coral accent · nav CTA only · no diagram · cleaner</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-c-proof.html">
          <span class="tag d">C-proof</span>
          <h2>Typography + diagram</h2>
          <p>Stagger · animated workflow diagram · grain · on live homepage now</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="section-title">Combinations — hero v2</p>
      <p class="intro" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: -0.5rem;">
        Mix of elements from all samples. Same copy everywhere. Pick a favorite or describe a mix.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-combo-1.html">
          <span class="tag b">Combo 1</span>
          <h2>Split + live UI</h2>
          <p>Split layout · real dashboard labels · amber badge pill · staggered reveal · “They build real tools”</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-combo-2.html">
          <span class="tag b">Combo 2</span>
          <h2>Stacked + atmosphere</h2>
          <p>Mesh background · larger headline · animated workflow diagram · coral glow · “Calm but not boring”</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-combo-3.html">
          <span class="tag d">Combo 3</span>
          <h2>Bold showcase</h2>
          <p>Split · animated metrics + chart · mesh + grain · badge pill · “Interactive systems”</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-combo-4.html">
          <span class="tag c">Combo 4</span>
          <h2>Typography-led</h2>
          <p>Largest headline · line stagger · mesh · minimal diagram · hero CTA button · “Design taste”</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="note">
        Reply with e.g. “Combo 3 motion + Combo 1 layout” or a single winner. We merge into the real homepage next.
      </p>

      <p class="section-title">Original samples</p>

      <div class="grid">
        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-a.html">
          <span class="tag">Sample A</span>
          <h2>Calm consultant</h2>
          <p>Split layout · workflow diagram · amber accent · nav links + CTA</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-b.html">
          <span class="tag b">Sample B</span>
          <h2>Quiet product</h2>
          <p>Stacked layout · dashboard mock · coral accent · CTA only in nav</p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/samples/hero-c.html">
          <span class="tag c">Sample C</span>
          <h2>Typography-first</h2>
          <p>Large headline · minimal visual · warm white CTA · soft mesh background</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="note" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 0; border-top: none;">
        Live homepage: <a href="/" style="color: #a8a5a0;">/</a> (C-proof — typography + diagram)
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
